"609","consideration of the Fund&#8217;s internal control over financial reporting was for"
"610","the limited purpose described in the first paragraph and would not necessarily"
"611","disclose all deficiencies in internal control that might be material weaknesses"
"612","under standards established by the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board"
